      <section id="details">
        <h2 class="gem-c-heading gem-c-heading--font-size-27 gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  ">Details</h2>


        
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
    
          <div class="govspeak">
<p>These letters set out the details of <a href="https://www.gov.uk/guidance/adult-education-budget-aeb-devolution" class="govuk-link">adult education budget (<abbr title="adult education budge">AEB</abbr>)</a> grant payments from 1 August 2020 to 31 July 2021.</p>

<p>This follows the devolution of the <abbr title="adult education budge">AEB</abbr> to Mayoral Combined Authorities and the Greater London Authority.</p>

<p>Payments will be made as section 31 grants. The Secretary of State for Education makes grant determinations under section 31 of the <a rel="external" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2003/26" class="govuk-link">Local Government Act 2003</a>.</p>

</div>

</div>
      </section>
    </div>

